entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You've begun your adventures in Star Wars Galaxies. It may be a dark path you begin on, but what you do from here is up to you. This is your story!
entries.journal_entry_description: Boba Fett has has warned you about helping Han on Tansarii station. Apparently Jabba has taken notice of you and thinks you owe him some form of debt. Boba Fett says you should meet with Vourk who he says may have a plan to help you get out of this situation.
entries.task00_comm_message_text: I hear Jabba's not too happy that you helped out Han Solo. You better go see Vourk in Mos Eisley. Maybe he can find you a way out of this mess.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Boba Fett says Jabba is looking for you and Vourk can help you out. It would be a good idea to talk to Vourk before Jabba's men find you.
